\c 5
\s Inzalo kaRubeni
\p
\v 1 Njalo amadodana kaRubeni, izibulo likaIsrayeli (ngoba wayelizibulo\x + Gen. 29.32. 49.3.\x*, kodwa njengoba wayengcolise umbheda kayise\x + Gen. 35.22. 49.4.\x*, ubuzibulo bakhe banikwa amadodana kaJosefa indodana kaIsrayeli\x + Gen. 48.15-22.\x*; futhi wayengabhalwanga njengezibulo;
\v 2 ngoba uJuda wayelamandla kulabafowabo, lowayengumbusi wavela kuye, kodwa ubuzibulo babungobukaJosefa\x + Gen. 49.8-10.\x*).
\v 3 Amadodana kaRubeni, izibulo likaIsrayeli: OHanoki, loPalu, uHezironi, loKarmi\x + Gen. 46.9. Eks. 6.14. Nani 26.5,6.\x*.
\v 4 Amadodana kaJoweli: UShemaya indodana yakhe, uGogi indodana yakhe, uShimeyi indodana yakhe,
\v 5 uMika indodana yakhe, uReyaya indodana yakhe, uBhali indodana yakhe,
\v 6 uBehera indodana yakhe, uTiligathi-Pilineseri inkosi yeAsiriya eyamthumbayo; wayeyisiphathamandla sabakoRubeni.
\v 7 Njalo abafowabo ngensendo zabo, lapho bebhalwa ngokwezizukulwana zabo\x + 5.17.\x*, bayizinhloko: OJeyiyeli, loZekhariya,
\v 8 loBhela indodana kaAzazi indodana kaShema indodana kaJoweli, owayehlala eAroweri\x + Dute. 2.36.\x*, njalo kwaze kwaba seNebo\x + Nani 32.3.\x* leBhali-Meyoni\x + Nani 32.38. Josh. 13.17. Hez. 25.9.\x*.
\v 9 Langempumalanga wahlala kwaze kwaba sekungeneni kwenkangala kusukela emfuleni iYufrathi, ngoba izifuyo zabo zasezandile elizweni leGileyadi\x + Josh. 22.9.\x*.
\v 10 Ensukwini zikaSawuli balawula-ke impi lamaHagari\x + 5.19,20. 11.38. 27.31. Hlab. 83.6. Gen. 25.12. 2 Sam. 24. 6.\x*, awa ngesandla sabo; bahlala emathenteni awo elizweni lonke lempumalanga yeGileyadi.
\s Inzalo kaGadi
\p
\v 11 Labantwana bakoGadi bahlala maqondana labo elizweni leBashani kwaze kwaba seSaleka\x + Josh. 12.5.\x*.
\v 12 UJoweli inhloko, loShafamu owesibili, loJanayi loShafati eBashani.
\v 13 Labafowabo ngendlu yaboyise: OMikayeli loMeshulamu loShebha loJorayi loJakani loZiya loEberi, beyisikhombisa.
\v 14 Laba babengamadodana kaAbihayili indodana kaHuri indodana kaJarowa indodana kaGileyadi indodana kaMikayeli indodana kaJeshishayi indodana kaJahido indodana kaBuzi.
\v 15 UAhi indodana kaAbidiyeli indodana kaGuni wayeyinhloko yendlu yaboyise.
\v 16 Basebehlala eGileyadi, eBashani, lemizaneni yayo, lakuwo wonke amadlelo eSharoni\x + 27.29. Josh. 12.18.\x*, kwaze kwaba sekuphumeni kwawo.
\v 17 Bonke laba babhalwa ngezizukulwana zabo ezinsukwini zikaJothamu inkosi yakoJuda\x + 2 Kho. 15.5,32.\x* lensukwini zikaJerobhowamu inkosi yakoIsrayeli\x + 2 Kho. 14.16,28.\x*.
\s Isizwe sakoRubeni lesakoGadi lengxenye yesizwe sakoManase
\p
\v 18 Amadodana kaRubeni labakoGadi lengxenye yesizwe sakoManase, emadodeni angamaqhawe, athwala isihlangu lenkemba, anyathela idandili, lezingcitshi empini\x + 8.40. 2 Lan. 14.8. Hlab. 7.13. 11. 2.\x*, ayeyizinkulungwane ezingamatshumi amane lane lamakhulu ayisikhombisa lamatshumi ayisithupha, ephumela ebuthweni\x + Nani 1.3.\x*.
\v 19 Basebelawula impi lamaHagari\x + 5.10.\x* loJeturi\x + 1.31. Gen. 25.15.\x* loNafishi loNodabi\x + 1.31. Gen. 25.15.\x*.
\v 20 Bancediswa bemelene labo, amaHagari asenikelwa esandleni sabo, labo bonke ababelawo; ngoba bakhala kuNkulunkulu besempini, wasencengeka ngabo\x + 2 Lan. 18.31. 2 Lan. 14.11.\x*, ngoba bamthemba\x + Hlab. 22.4. 25.2.\x*.
\v 21 Bathumba izifuyo zabo, amakamela azinkulungwane ezingamatshumi amahlanu, lezimvu ezizinkulungwane ezingamakhulu amabili lamatshumi amahlanu, labobabhemi abazinkulungwane ezimbili, lemiphefumulo yabantu ezinkulungwane ezilikhulu.
\v 22 Ngoba kwawa abanengi ababuleweyo, ngoba impi yayingekaNkulunkulu. Basebehlala ezindaweni zabo\x + 4.41.\x* kwaze kwafika ukuthunjwa\x + 5.6,25. 2 Kho. 15.29. 17.6.\x*.
\p
\v 23 Abantwana bengxenye yesizwe sakoManase basebehlala elizweni; kusukela eBashani kusiya eBhali-Hermoni leSeniri\x + Hez. 27.5. Dute. 3.9.\x* lentabeni yeHermoni bona banda\x + Hez. 27.5. Dute. 3.9.\x*.
\v 24 Lalezi zinhloko zendlu yaboyise, ngitsho oEferi loIshi loEliyeli loAziriyeli loJeremiya loHodaviya loJahidiyeli, amadoda angamaqhawe alamandla, amadoda alamabizo, inhloko zendlu yaboyise.
\p
\v 25 Kodwa bona kuNkulunkulu waboyise, baphinga \add ngo\add*kulandela onkulunkulu babantu balelolizwe, uNkulunkulu abachithayo phambi kwabo\x + 2 Kho. 17.7. Eks. 34.15.\x*.
\v 26 Ngakho uNkulunkulu kaIsrayeli wavusa umoya kaPhuli inkosi yeAsiriya\x + 2 Kho. 15.19.\x*, lomoya kaTiligathi-Pilineseri inkosi yeAsiriya\x + 2 Kho. 15.29. 2 Kho. 16.7.\x*, wabathumba, ngitsho abakoRubeni labakoGadi lengxenye yesizwe sakoManase, wabasa eHala\x + 2 Kho. 17.6.\x* leHabori\x + 2 Kho. 17.6.\x* leHara lemfuleni iGozani\x + 2 Kho. 17.6.\x*, kuze kube lamuhla.
